	   <tr><td colspan=2>You have to give your pets two one-handed weapons to make them hit 4 times in a round. Pets will hit twice from having two weapons equiped, and then two more times for having the double attack ability. At your level they will rarely actually hit 4 times in a round however. It still helps though, and weapons look cool, so just summon a few.<br><br>Former EQ Addict that is playing again.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
