	   <tr><td colspan=2>You've never even TRIED two of our best pets and you talk about how much you know. <br>Fire ROCKS for soloing from about 29 and on, the DS kills things quickly and efficiently, and it's easier to get full XP for the mob because DS damage is "neutral" and counts against neither you nor your pet. But DS damage AGGRO counts against your pet making it less likely to overaggro.<br>Water is good for soloing, MUCH better than earth. They have less HP sure, but the mob actually misses them once in a while. And they have the HP of earth once you focus them. <br>ALSO: Grouping IS better than soloing. Trust me, you'll thank me once you get to 30 or so and the mobs start tearing through your pets like tissue paper.<br><br>THe grumpy gnome, Xev server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
