	   <tr><td colspan=2>My recently new mage is now level 4 and has the pet spells, so I have some questions (assuming doing a solo):<br><br>1) getting exp: does it matter who does most of the damage? if the pet does ALL of the damage, do you get the same exp as if you did all of the damage?<br><br>2) can the pet use any type of weapon (1hs, piercing, etc)?<br><br>3) melee skills: with my other chars, I try to work my skills (1hs, 1hb, etc). But if the pet does most of the work, does that mean my melee skills will be awfull forever? Or does my skill not matter since the pets should be the one fighting?<br><br>4) is there such a thing as the pet's melee skill? ie: do the pet get better only if they melee a lot? or are their skills based on the level of the spell used to conjure them up?<br><br>Thanks...seems like the mage class will be pretty fun!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
