	   <tr><td colspan=2>I know you said you were a newbie, but 20th level and you don't know how to get rid of your pet?  Ok, here is the most important thing a mage can do.  LEARN your pet commands, like /pet get lost will cause your pet to be dismissed.  If you don't learn to controll your pet, no one will want to group with you.  The reason for this is your pet might pull more than is safe for the group and endanger innocents around you.  Just go to Everquest.com and check the game manual, it has the pet commands listed there.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
