	   <tr><td colspan=2>Twink comes from "Twinkie"<br>The seemingly invincible pastry (?)<br>(to Quote Apu from Simpsons after a twinkie reforms from being squooshed: "You can not destroy the Twinkie!") with the soft, creamy middle.<br><br>Tough on the outside (covered with high level gear/high resists/boosted stats/etc), but on the inside...and soft and vulnerable on the outside.<br>&nbsp;<br>Astralyte, Druid 37 - Xev<br>Astrall,VS Beastlord - Xev</td></tr>
